videos.description: Sacar Anim tracks down a loose ball and gets it to Andrew Rowsey who makes the three-point shot.
videos.headline: Marquette answers with Rowsey 3-pointer

videos.description: Jamal Cain makes a break and finishes it off with a slam for Marquette.
videos.headline: Cain capitalizes on turnover with slam

videos.description: Rashard Kelly shuts down a pair of Marquette shots in the first half.
videos.headline: Kelly comes up with back-to-back blocks

videos.description: Andrew Rowsey beats his defender as he sinks a long jumper.
videos.headline: Rowsey makes tough jumper

videos.description: Austin Reaves gets a pass to Rauno Nurger who finishes it with a slam for Wichita State.
videos.headline: Reaves connects with Nurger for dunk

videos.description: Darral Willis Jr. gets a nice block to shut down a Marquette possession in the second half.
videos.headline: Willis gets big block

videos.description: Markus Howard sinks a 3-pointer to bring Marquette within two possessions of Wichita State in the second half.
videos.headline: Howard reaches 25 points with 3-pointer

videos.description: Austin Reaves drives to the basket and spins around his defender to make a bucket.
videos.headline: Reaves uses sweet spin move on layup

videos.description: Rashard Kelly, who nearly posted a triple-double, says Wichita State has to keep focusing on rebounding and defense to have success this season.
videos.headline: Kelly proud of the way his team played vs. Marquette
